---
import Layout from '../layouts/Page.astro';
import '../styles/oz-custom.css';
---

<Layout>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="oz-hero">
		<div class="oz-hero-content">
			<h1>Opportunity Zone Tax Benefits</h1>
			<p class="subtitle">Maximize your tax savings with strategic OZ investment planning</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Tax Benefits Overview -->
	<section class="oz-services">
		<div class="oz-services-content">
			<div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
				<h2>Three Powerful Tax Benefits of Opportunity Zone Investments</h2>
				<p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--oz-gray-600); margin-bottom: 3rem;">
					Opportunity Zone investments offer three distinct tax advantages that can significantly reduce your tax burden while generating strong returns. Understanding these benefits is crucial for maximizing your investment potential.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="oz-services-grid">
				<div class="oz-service-card">
					<div class="icon">⏰</div>
					<h3>1. Capital Gains Deferral</h3>
					<p>Defer paying capital gains taxes until December 31, 2026, or when you sell your OZ investment, whichever comes first.</p>
					<ul style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1rem;">
						<li>Defer taxes on capital gains from any source</li>
						<li>Must invest within 180 days of gain realization</li>
						<li>Taxes due by December 31, 2026</li>
						<li>No limit on deferral amount</li>
					</ul>
					<div style="background: var(--oz-gray-50); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
						<strong>Example:</strong> $1M capital gain → Defer $200K in taxes until 2026
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="oz-service-card">
					<div class="icon">📈</div>
					<h3>2. Basis Step-Up</h3>
					<p>Reduce your deferred capital gains by 10% after 5 years and an additional 5% after 7 years, for a total 15% reduction.</p>
					<ul style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1rem;">
						<li>5-year hold: 10% basis step-up</li>
						<li>7-year hold: Additional 5% (15% total)</li>
						<li>Must hold until December 31, 2026</li>
						<li>Maximum 15% reduction on deferred gains</li>
					</ul>
					<div style="background: var(--oz-gray-50); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
						<strong>Example:</strong> $1M gain → Pay taxes on only $850K after 7 years
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="oz-service-card">
					<div class="icon">🎯</div>
					<h3>3. Tax-Free Appreciation</h3>
					<p>Eliminate capital gains taxes on appreciation if you hold your OZ investment for at least 10 years.</p>
					<ul style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1rem;">
						<li>Must hold for 10+ years</li>
						<li>Tax-free appreciation on OZ investment</li>
						<li>No limit on appreciation amount</li>
						<li>Must sell by December 31, 2047</li>
					</ul>
					<div style="background: var(--oz-gray-50); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
						<strong>Example:</strong> $1M investment → $3M value after 10 years → $2M appreciation tax-free
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Tax Planning Strategies -->
	<section class="oz-authority">
		<div class="oz-authority-content">
			<h2>Strategic Tax Planning for OZ Investments</h2>
			<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem;">
				<div style="background: var(--oz-white); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: var(--oz-shadow);">
					<h3 style="color: var(--oz-navy); margin-bottom: 1rem;">⏰ Timing Optimization</h3>
					<p>Strategic timing of your OZ investment can maximize tax benefits:</p>
					<ul style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1rem;">
						<li>Invest before December 31, 2021 for full 7-year benefits</li>
						<li>Consider market conditions and property availability</li>
						<li>Plan for December 31, 2026 tax payment</li>
						<li>Optimize for 10-year hold period</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				
				<div style="background: var(--oz-white); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: var(--oz-shadow);">
					<h3 style="color: var(--oz-navy); margin-bottom: 1rem;">💰 Gain Source Strategy</h3>
					<p>Different types of capital gains can be optimized for OZ investment:</p>
					<ul style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1rem;">
						<li>Stock market gains</li>
						<li>Real estate sale proceeds</li>
						<li>Business sale proceeds</li>
						<li>Cryptocurrency gains</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				
				<div style="background: var(--oz-white); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: var(--oz-shadow);">
					<h3 style="color: var(--oz-navy); margin-bottom: 1rem;">🏛️ Fund vs. Direct Investment</h3>
					<p>Choose the right investment structure for your situation:</p>
					<ul style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1rem;">
						<li>QOF for diversification and professional management</li>
						<li>Direct investment for control and higher returns</li>
						<li>Consider your expertise and time availability</li>
						<li>Evaluate fees and management structure</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Tax Calculator -->
	<section class="oz-tools">
		<div class="oz-tools-content">
			<h2>OZ Tax Savings Calculator</h2>
			<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
				<div style="background: var(--oz-white); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: var(--oz-shadow-lg);">
					<h3 style="color: var(--oz-navy); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">Calculate Your Potential Tax Savings</h3>
					
					<div class="oz-form-group">
						<label class="oz-form-label">Capital Gains Amount</label>
						<input type="number" id="capital-gains" class="oz-form-input" placeholder="1000000">
					</div>
					
					<div class="oz-form-group">
						<label class="oz-form-label">Capital Gains Tax Rate (%)</label>
						<input type="number" id="tax-rate" class="oz-form-input" placeholder="20" value="20">
					</div>
					
					<div class="oz-form-group">
						<label class="oz-form-label">Investment Amount</label>
						<input type="number" id="investment-amount" class="oz-form-input" placeholder="1000000">
					</div>
					
					<div class="oz-form-group">
						<label class="oz-form-label">Expected Annual Return (%)</label>
						<input type="number" id="annual-return" class="oz-form-input" placeholder="8" value="8">
					</div>
					
					<button onclick="calculateTaxSavings()" class="oz-btn oz-btn-primary" style="width: 100%;">Calculate Tax Savings</button>
					
					<div id="tax-results" style="margin-top: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--oz-gray-50); border-radius: 0.375rem; display: none;">
						<h4 style="color: var(--oz-navy); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Tax Savings Analysis:</h4>
						<div id="tax-breakdown"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Case Study -->
	<section class="oz-testimonials">
		<div class="oz-testimonials-content">
			<h2>Tax Benefits Case Study</h2>
			<div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
				<div style="background: var(--oz-white); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: var(--oz-shadow);">
					<h3 style="color: var(--oz-navy); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">$5M Business Sale Tax Optimization</h3>
					<p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.125rem;">
						<strong>Situation:</strong> Tech entrepreneur sold company for $5M with $4M in capital gains
					</p>
					
					<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
						<div style="background: var(--oz-gray-50); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.375rem;">
							<h4 style="color: var(--oz-navy); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Without OZ Investment</h4>
							<ul style="text-align: left;">
								<li>Capital gains tax: $800K (20%)</li>
								<li>Net proceeds: $4.2M</li>
								<li>Investment amount: $4.2M</li>
								<li>10-year value: $9.1M</li>
								<li>Tax on appreciation: $980K</li>
								<li><strong>Net after taxes: $8.1M</strong></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						
						<div style="background: var(--oz-gold); color: var(--oz-white); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.375rem;">
							<h4 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">With OZ Investment</h4>
							<ul style="text-align: left;">
								<li>Deferred tax: $800K until 2026</li>
								<li>Basis step-up: $120K (15%)</li>
								<li>Investment amount: $5M</li>
								<li>10-year value: $10.8M</li>
								<li>Tax-free appreciation: $5.8M</li>
								<li><strong>Net after taxes: $9.9M</strong></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div style="background: var(--oz-navy); color: var(--oz-white); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; text-align: center;">
						<h4 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Total Tax Savings: $1.8M</h4>
						<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.125rem;">Additional return of 22% over 10 years</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA Section -->
	<section class="oz-cta">
		<div class="oz-cta-content">
			<h2>Ready to Maximize Your Tax Benefits?</h2>
			<p>Schedule a consultation with our tax specialists to develop a strategic OZ investment plan that maximizes your tax savings.</p>
			<div class="oz-hero .cta-buttons">
				<a href="/contact" class="oz-btn oz-btn-primary">Schedule Tax Consultation</a>
				<a href="/resources/guides" class="oz-btn oz-btn-secondary">Download Tax Guide</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<script>
	function calculateTaxSavings() {
		const capitalGains = parseFloat(document.getElementById('capital-gains').value);
		const taxRate = parseFloat(document.getElementById('tax-rate').value) / 100;
		const investmentAmount = parseFloat(document.getElementById('investment-amount').value);
		const annualReturn = parseFloat(document.getElementById('annual-return').value) / 100;
		
		if (!capitalGains || !taxRate || !investmentAmount || !annualReturn) {
			alert('Please fill in all fields');
			return;
		}
		
		// Calculate tax savings
		const immediateTax = capitalGains * taxRate;
		const deferredTax = immediateTax * 0.85; // 15% basis step-up
		const taxSavings = immediateTax - deferredTax;
		
		// Calculate investment returns
		const futureValue = investmentAmount * Math.pow(1 + annualReturn, 10);
		const appreciation = futureValue - investmentAmount;
		const appreciationTax = appreciation * taxRate;
		
		// Total benefits
		const totalTaxSavings = taxSavings + appreciationTax;
		const totalBenefit = totalTaxSavings / investmentAmount * 100;
		
		const resultsHTML = `
			<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
				<div style="background: var(--oz-white); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; text-align: center;">
					<h5 style="color: var(--oz-navy); margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">Immediate Tax Deferral</h5>
					<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--oz-gold);">$${immediateTax.toLocaleString()}</p>
				</div>
				<div style="background: var(--oz-white); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; text-align: center;">
					<h5 style="color: var(--oz-navy); margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">Basis Step-Up Savings</h5>
					<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--oz-gold);">$${taxSavings.toLocaleString()}</p>
				</div>
				<div style="background: var(--oz-white); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; text-align: center;">
					<h5 style="color: var(--oz-navy); margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">Tax-Free Appreciation</h5>
					<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--oz-gold);">$${appreciationTax.toLocaleString()}</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div style="background: var(--oz-navy); color: var(--oz-white); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; text-align: center;">
				<h4 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">Total Tax Savings</h4>
				<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700;">$${totalTaxSavings.toLocaleString()}</p>
				<p style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9;">${totalBenefit.toFixed(1)}% additional return over 10 years</p>
			</div>
		`;
		
		document.getElementById('tax-breakdown').innerHTML = resultsHTML;
		document.getElementById('tax-results').style.display = 'block';
	}
</script>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "name": "Opportunity Zone Tax Benefits",
  "description": "Maximize your tax savings with strategic OZ investment planning",
  "provider": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "OZ Specialist",
    "url": "https://opportunityzonespecialist.com"
  },
  "serviceType": "Tax Planning",
  "areaServed": "United States",
  "hasOfferCatalog": {
    "@type": "OfferCatalog",
    "name": "Tax Planning Services",
    "itemListElement": [
      {
        "@type": "Offer",
        "itemOffered": {
          "@type": "Service",
          "name": "Capital Gains Deferral"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Offer",
        "itemOffered": {
          "@type": "Service",
          "name": "Basis Step-Up Optimization"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Offer",
        "itemOffered": {
          "@type": "Service",
          "name": "Tax-Free Appreciation Planning"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
</script>
